<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lù shì zhǔ suǒ pù 迦南1132</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lù shì zhǔ suǒ pù ya, mén shì zhǔ dǎ kāi.
 dēng shì zhǔ diǎn liàng ya, zhǒng zi tǔ xià mái.
 zhuāng jià duō yòu duō ya, yuǎn fāng yǒu hū shēng.
 wǒ men dāng qiú zhuāng jià de zhǔ, pài gōng rén shōu gē.
 xiàng qián zǒu bù huí tóu,
 tóng gān kǔ xié qǐ shǒu.
 zhǔ yǐn dǎo yǒu guāng kě jiù.
 zhǔ bì zhòng xiū huāng fèi de chéng yì, zài jīn qiū.
 zhǔ bì zhòng xiū huāng fèi de chéng yì, zài jīn qiū.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1132</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>